Ignition Analyzer

Look for:

    Timing advance at cruise
    Timing pull under load

Flag:

    Excessive knock retard
    Unusual timing behavior

MAP Sensor Analyzer

Important values:

Warm Idle

    Usually around 25–40 kPa

2500 RPM No Load

    Usually lower than idle

Wide Open Throttle

    Near atmospheric pressure (~95–100 kPa depending on altitude)

Flag anything abnormal.
